{"id":265513,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-安吉叶根来举报违法征地遭报复，屋尖被/","date":"2012-11-27T21:45:48Z","modified":"2012-11-27T21:45:48Z","title":"维权网 | 安吉叶根来举报违法征地遭报复，屋尖被拆除（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员安民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span>左右，浙江省安吉县城管派大批人马将该县递铺镇荷花塘村农民叶根来家刚修好的屋尖强行拆除，水泥砖全部打烂。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>叶根来修缮屋顶于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年经过荷花塘村村委和递铺镇政府批准，后因其和村民一起举报安吉县经济开发区违法征地受政府报复，不准其盖屋顶。十八大前叶根来被递铺镇政府强制到新疆阿克苏“旅游”。前几天因在网上披露当地政府官员强占农民土地造别墅，再次受到政府报复。政府不去查处违法建造别墅的官员，却强拆农民为防止漏雨而修缮的屋顶，完全不顾公民的居住权和生存权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>城管本来是一个管理城市市容市貌的机构，本身不具有执法的法律地位，安吉县政府竟通过住建局、规划局、国土局等“授权”城管去管理农村的农民集体土地，使城管的权力无限膨胀，严重违反了国家法律。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-luh2d6q9wek/ULTbQSxkpiI/AAAAAAAAUWE/mxzz1rQORl4/s1600/img010_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-luh2d6q9wek/ULTbQSxkpiI/AAAAAAAAUWE/mxzz1rQORl4/s320/img010_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rnMbOTrqquo/ULTbVX7PlFI/AAAAAAAAUWM/f3DDjaKA_iE/s1600/img011_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rnMbOTrqquo/ULTbVX7PlFI/AAAAAAAAUWM/f3DDjaKA_iE/s320/img011_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-U0L9YVfPFwM/ULTbWin0wTI/AAAAAAAAUWU/uXSJB6jvx5A/s1600/img012_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-U0L9YVfPFwM/ULTbWin0wTI/AAAAAAAAUWU/uXSJB6jvx5A/s320/img012_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1257264511707720698?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}